Anglo American Platinum’s (Amplat’s) large-scale Mogalakwena mine, located on the Northern Limb of the Bushveld Complex, is the type of asset every PGM miner wants to operate. And while it already occupies the platinum major’s flagship status within its entire asset portfolio, CEO CHRIS GRIFFITH tells LAURA CORNISH that the company continues to evaluate the potential to enhance the operation’s performance further – through optimisation initiatives, the incorporation of digital technologies and even possibly a further expansion.